categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Oh'dvek was a male Human who served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic as a Jedi Master during the Galactic War with the Sith Empire. Master Oh'dvek equipped Jedi Consulars with gear on Keylander Station during the Conquest of Makeb, as well as during the Seizure of CZ-198, inside the Czerka Corporation facility CZ-198
